-- Reliance Broadcast Network Shares Gain on Plan to Form Venture With CBS
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-06-21T03:46:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/reliance-broadcast-network-shares-gain-on-plan-to-form-venture-with-cbs.html

          
          
             Reliance Broadcast Network Ltd.
gained as much as 5.1 percent in Mumbai trading after saying it
plans to form a venture with a unit of CBS Corp. to operate
television channels in India and neighboring South Asian
countries.  
          
          


  


        